<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[269,492,1627,1654]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" refId="ref369190" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena, 99 pp., 1 pl. [This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a)]." type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863: 68)</bibRefCitation>
